text: Iotated Yat (majuscule: ⟨Ꙓ⟩, minuscule: ⟨ꙓ⟩) is a Cyrillic character combining a decimal I and a yat. There was no numerical value for this letter and it was not in the Glagolitic alphabet. It was encoded in Unicode 5.1 at positions U+A652 and U+A653. Category:Cyrillic letters
title: Iotated Yat
